An extension of the univariate [[Taylor expansion]] to [[Multivariate calculus]]:

$$f(x+\delta x) = f(x)+\nabla^T f(x) \delta x + \frac{1}{2} \delta x^T H(x) \delta x$$ $$ + \text{higher order terms}$$

where $$H$$ is the [[Hessian]]